Package com.satori.rtm

RTM client and connection classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Callback<V>
    A callback for any asynchronous call that can result in success or failure.
    RtmClient
    An RtmClient is the main entry point for accessing RTM.
    RtmClientListener
    Defines callback methods for events in the RTM client lifecycle.
    SubscriptionListener
    Defines callback methods for events in the subscription lifecycle.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RtmClientAdapter
    An empty implementation of the RtmClientListener interface.
    RtmClientBuilder
    An RtmClient builder class.
    SubscriptionAdapter
    An empty implementation of the SubscriptionListener interface.
    SubscriptionConfig
    Provides settings that configure a subscription.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Ack
    Defines the acknowledgement mode for RTM operations.
    SubscriptionMode  

Package com.satori.rtm Description

RTM client and connection classes. Use RtmClientBuilder to create an RTM client.
